article.description: — Will Martinez scored 18 points with eight rebounds off the bench to carry Wagner to a 77-59 wire-to-wire win over Hartford on Tuesday night in a season opener for both teams.
article.headline: Martinez scores 18 to carry Wagner past Hartford 77-59
article.linkText: Martinez scores 18 to carry Wagner past Hartford 77-59
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Will Martinez scored 18 points with eight rebounds off the bench to carry Wagner to a 77-59 wire-to-wire win over Hartford on Tuesday night in a season opener for both teams. Martinez made 8 of 10 shots. He added eight defensive rebounds. Alex Morales had 15 points for Wagner. Raekwon Rogers added 10 points. Jared Kimbrough had 13 points for the Hawks. Moses Flowers added 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
